c=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然俾豐田食咗<br />\n但佢原身唔係日廠<br />\n佢仍然保留緊自已嘅品牌"},{"pid":"72bd4519f84ce9c8d24ba3564b6a7cbc75eafb7c","tid":111950,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有錢=歐洲車<br />\n冇錢=日本車<br />\n<br />\n歐洲=鋼水好，食油好，零件費用都一樣好<br />\n日本=鋼水差，食油細，零件費用都一樣細<br />\n<br />\n歐洲維修=返廠啦屌你，買零件都要訂<br />\n日本維修=街邊都有行貨零件，基本上好少要訂<br />\n<br />\n做人唔可以貪心，有得必有失</blockquote><br />\n咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歐洲 turbo 車馬力又大又慳油，除非新車岩岩出，唔係周街都有副廠件/副廠 sensor 換啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本車想要重少少安全少少（但冇turbo），仲有Mazda 比你簡，雙田咪加錢買新D，加錢咪多D氣袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行貨真係冇，仲有水貨日本車多D氣袋</blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\nToyota Sienta 新車都係雙氣袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直在玩命"},{"pid":"9cb661c52d4794911aeb41aa3aaf4f28cbfb3b25","tid":111950,"uid":34109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:48:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有錢=歐洲車<br />\n冇錢=日本車<br />\n<br />\n歐洲=鋼水好，食油好，零件費用都一樣好<br />\n日本=鋼水差，食油細，零件費用都一樣細<br />\n<br />\n歐洲維修=返廠啦屌你，買零件都要訂<br />\n日本維修=街邊都有行貨零件，基本上好少要訂<br />\n<br />\n做人唔可以貪心，有得必有失</blockquote><br />\nLexus鋼水都差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然俾豐田食咗<br />\n但佢原身唔係日廠<br />\n佢仍然保留緊自已嘅品牌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n恕我才疏學淺<br />\nlexus唔係都係Toyota個founder Eiji Toyoda成立嘅咩"},{"pid":"8f9e352eee73c64541757bf74720b4faea83e8e7","tid":111950,"uid":46700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor